<div class="music-list" style="margin-top:20px;"><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/7fingers.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/7fingers.jpg" alt="7fingers / Nils Frahm" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/7fingers.php">7fingers<br />Nils Frahm</a></h4><p>さわやかなストリングスと繊細なエレクトロな音色が絶妙にブレンドされていて、とても心地よい作品です。控えめに鳴るピアノの音色も早朝にはぴったりで何度でも聴きたくなる作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003NWS5GI?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003NWS5GI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', '7fingers-Nils Frahm']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252F7fingers%252Fid378029869%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', '7fingers-Nils Frahm']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/a-permanent-solution.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/permanentso.jpg" alt="A Permanent Solution / Proem" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/a-permanent-solution.php">A Permanent Solution<br />Proem</a></h4><p>重苦しくないライトなイメージのある作品。ゆったりとしたテンポの楽曲が多く、ウォーミングアップとして朝に聴くのに適した作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000P1KP0E?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000P1KP0E" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'A Permanent Solution-Proem']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fa-permanent-solution%252Fid255464328%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'A Permanent Solution-Proem']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/voiceband-jilt.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/voiceband.jpg" alt="Voiceband Jilt / Gregory Taylor" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/voiceband-jilt.php">Voiceband Jilt<br />Gregory Taylor</a></h4><p>眠いときにゆっくりと目を覚ますのに聴くとよさそうな音楽です。ゆったりとした中にも躍動感があるため、ゆっくりと始動するには最適な音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000GBE7NE?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000GBE7NE" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Voiceband Jilt-Gregory Taylor']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fvoiceband-jilt%252Fid265404986%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Voiceband Jilt-Gregory Taylor']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/exp.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/exp.jpg" alt="EXP / Frank Bretschneider" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/exp.php">EXP<br />Frank Bretschneider</a></h4><p>生活の中に溶け込んでしまいそうな音がたくさん含まれている音楽です。じわじわと刺激を与えてくれるエレクトロニカ作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003EURA92?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003EURA92" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'EXP-Frank Bretschneider']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fexp%252Fid372532174%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'EXP-Frank Bretschneider']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/volume-objects.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/volumeobject.jpg" alt="Volume Objects / Autistici" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/volume-objects.php">Volume Objects<br />Autistici</a></h4><p>朝、起きたすぐで何もやる気が起きないとき聴きたくなる作品です。適度に緊張感があるため、1日の中でやりたいことを考えるのにもよいでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0015FK0I6?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0015FK0I6" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Volume Objects-Autistici']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fvolume-objects%252Fid270436120%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Volume Objects-Autistici']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/lupe-luep-peul-epul.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/lupeluep.jpg" alt="Lupe Luep Peul Epul / Miki Yui" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/lupe-luep-peul-epul.php">Lupe Luep Peul Epul<br />Miki Yui</a></h4><p>体調があまりよくない時や気分が乗らないときでも不思議と相性の合う作品。耳に痛い高音などはほとんど入っていないため、邪魔にならないBGMと言えるでしょう。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B00005YBWJ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B00005YBWJ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Lupe Luep Peul Epul-Miki Yui']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Flupe-luep-peul-epul%252Fid287484937%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Lupe Luep Peul Epul-Miki Yui']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/i-hold-a-wish-for-you.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/iholdawishofryou.jpg" alt="I Hold a Wish for You / aspidistrafly" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/i-hold-a-wish-for-you.php">I Hold a Wish for You<br />aspidistrafly</a></h4><p>絶対に朝に聴きたい。と思わせるような作品。アコースティックギターや女性ヴォーカルの優しい音色が早朝にとても合う美しい作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002S4DMWE?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002S4DMWE" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'I Hold a Wish for You-aspidistrafly']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fi-hold-a-wish-for-you%252Fid309296310%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'I Hold a Wish for You-aspidistrafly']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/the-elektronik-soft-heart-of-my-teknomodal-poet.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/electronik.jpg" alt="The Elektronik Soft Heart of My Teknomodal Poet / Climnoizer" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/the-elektronik-soft-heart-of-my-teknomodal-poet.php">The Elektronik Soft Heart of My Teknomodal Poet<br />Climnoizer</a></h4><p>少し元気がある朝にはこの作品もよいです。ジャズやファンクを感じさせる少し変則的なエレクトニックサウンドです。朝食のBGMとして聴くのもよいと思います。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B003C0Q84M?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B003C0Q84M" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'The Elektronik Soft Heart of My Teknomodal Poet-Climnoizer']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fthe-elektronik-soft-heart%252Fid352112938%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'The Elektronik Soft Heart of My Teknomodal Poet-Climnoizer']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/pale-ravine.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/paleravine.jpg" alt="Pale Ravine / Deaf Center" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/07/pale-ravine.php">Pale Ravine<br />Deaf Center</a></h4><p>旅行に行った時や、いつもと違う気分のときにかけたくなる音楽です。朝の景色を見ながら少し大きめの音で聴きたくなる躍動的な音楽です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B000CDYDPI?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B000CDYDPI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Pale Ravine-Deaf Center']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fpale-ravine%252Fid276144188%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Pale Ravine-Deaf Center']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target